# Snowflake Project Tree

```
02-snowflake-warehouse/
├── sql/
│   ├── setup/
│   │   ├── 01_create_warehouses.sql
│   │   ├── 02_create_databases.sql
│   │   └── 03_create_schemas.sql
│   ├── procedures/              # Stored procedures/functions
│   ├── views/                   # SQL views
│   └── tasks/                   # Scheduled Snowflake tasks
├── roles_and_permissions/
│   ├── roles.sql                # Role and permission configurations
│   └── user_setup.sql
├── documentation/
│   ├── data_dictionary.md       # Data catalog
│   └── maintenance_guide.md
├── monitoring/
│   ├── query_performance.sql    # Performance monitoring
│   └── cost_tracking.sql
├── .sqlfluff                    # SQL linting rules
└── README.md
```

## Setup Instructions

1. Update Snowflake credentials
2. Execute setup scripts: `01_create_warehouses.sql` → `02_create_databases.sql` → `03_create_schemas.sql`
3. Set up roles and permissions: `roles_and_permissions/roles.sql`
4. Monitor with queries in `monitoring/query_performance.sql`

## Key Components

- **Warehouses**: analytics_wh, etl_wh, reporting_wh
- **Layers**: Bronze (raw), Silver (cleaned), Gold (business-ready)
- **Security**: Role-based access control (RBAC)
